                <mxCell id="takeaways" value="1) Takeaways (3-4 bullets)&lt;br&gt;What goes here: highest-value claims in 10 seconds.&lt;br&gt;Why: fast payoff and skim value." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
