                <mxCell id="summary" value="3) Storyline (flowing, 3-4 chunks / slides)&lt;br&gt;What goes here: core thesis + practical interpretation in one smooth narrative.&lt;br&gt;Why: depth without fragmenting into tiny sections.&lt;br&gt;Rule: no meta phrasing (&quot;this video explains&quot;), no bullet artifacts inside prose." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
