                <mxCell id="2" value="1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Summary&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(3-4 sentences)&lt;div&gt;Capture the overall theme for the video. Should be in a user friendly tone such that user can get a grasp of idea videa about the video. Its should not descibe &quot;what will you get from this video&quot; (thats, what ge got the Takeaways to), but instead it should introduce the topics and concepts in the video, such that even users unfamiliar with the topics get an understanding&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffcd28;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;gradientColor=#ffa500;" parent="1" vertex="1">
